    "Paraphrasing demanded more than mere substitution of synonyms; it required a substantial transformation of the original text while preserving its core meaning [3].",
    "Therefore, the framework of plagiarism, rooted in the clear demarcation of original and borrowed material, served as a cornerstone in academic writing.",
